          "action": "escalate_to_human",
          "handoffTarget": "dispatch_supervisor",
          "rationale": "Two misses puts the order into customer-detractor and potential PUC service-quality-metric territory; a supervisor must lock a guaranteed window and confirm technician skill match rather than letting auto-scheduling retry."
        }
